{
  "texts": [
    "And walking the prisoners is walking that is meant for them but against their will.",
    "\"Walk\" can mean importantly different things.",
    "Professional linguists can tease out these differences grammatically in the nuances of transitivity, mood, voice, case, and more.",
    "Yet even when we don't have the technical words for it, we know the differences.",
    "People do grammar in their brains, sometimes consciously but mostly unconsciously."
  ]
}